==古生物学==
发现该属化石的岩石可能代表[[风蚀|风蚀]]沙丘及丘间环境，具有小型时令湖和季节性溪流，由此可知多智龙是种[[沙漠|沙漠]]动物；另一方面可能也存在水源充足的森林。多智龙可能被[[特暴龙|特暴龙]]捕食。<ref name="Paul2010"/> 
===古病理学===
一个多智龙骨显示出[[暴龙科|暴龙科]]的特暴龙的咬痕，表明该兽脚类捕食了这只甲龙科。<ref>{{cite book|last=Holtz, Jr.|first=Thomas|title=Dinosaurs: the most complete, up-to-date encyclopedia for dinosaur lovers of all ages|date=2007|publisher=Random House, Inc.|location=New York, New York|isbn=9780375824197|page=[https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/241 241]|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/241}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | last = Gallagher | first =W. B. | last2 = Tumanova | first2 = T. A. | last3 = Dodson | first3 = P. | last4 = Axel | first4 = L. | year = 1998 | title = CT scanning Asian ankylosaurs: paleopathology in a ''Tarchia'' skull | journal = Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology | volume = 18 | pages = 44A–45A}}</ref>

